  06 Nov 2003; root <root@gentoo.org> kdemultimedia-3.2.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Remove cdr use flag (see bug 24169)

  05 Nov 2003; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> kdemultimedia-3.2.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Block juk as it's in this package now.
  Drop cdrtools/cdrdao support (see bugs #32792 and #24169)
  Drop xanim as aKtion frontend is gone.
  Thank to Gregorio Guidi for pointing these out

  04 Nov 2003; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> kdemultimedia-3.2.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Add gstreamer use flag and dependency

